4. HARDWARE TRACKING & ANTI-RESALE FEATURES

   The hardware fingerprinting, TPM tracking, IMEI logging, and resale-
   detection features of this software are intended exclusively for:

   (a) Recovering stolen company-owned assets;
   (b) Preventing unauthorized resale of company equipment;
   (c) Enforcing corporate device lifecycle policies.

   These features MUST NOT be used to track privately-owned devices or
   hardware outside the enrolled device inventory of the deploying organization.

5. ENROLLMENT CONSENT REQUIREMENT

   Any device enrolled in this system must display a clear, prominent notice
   to the device user prior to or at the time of enrollment, disclosing:

   (a) That the device is subject to remote monitoring and management;
   (b) What data is collected and how it is used;
   (c) The identity of the organization managing the device.

   Enrollment without such notice may violate applicable laws.

